DESCRIPTION

 The installation script prepares startup files and copy Bismark files to /root after mounting it on /dev/hda2.

 It has only been tested with the official 0.5.0 image.

PREREQUISITES

 A second partition should be created on the flash card (/dev/hda2)

INSTALLATION

 Assuming the default configuration provided by the official 0.5.0 image:

 - Run the installation script specifying the name to be assigned to the box: 

	./install boxname

   The boxname can be a string up to 15 characters.

